{"tid":1545162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中共一早已經計劃好搵前線popo做替死鬼","createTime":"2019-09-05T23:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T00:05:49.000Z","uid":275926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef16fee6a768a39ffc5462f8f2ba86d5fe2f773","tid":1545162,"uid":275926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:15:08.000Z","msg":"Background:<br />\n<br />\n中共一向信奉「槍桿子出政權」，要有效管治就要嚴格控制當地武裝力量<br />\n<br />\n香港唯一合法武裝力量係警隊（駐港解放軍唔算，因為只能用來做主權象徵，實際上唔用得。）<br />\n<br />\n中共起警隊入面安插同招攬培養「自己人」，直接影響控制警察已經係半公開秘密。無論邊個做特首，警隊實際都唔受CE控制，所以可以跋扈到無視張建宗。<br />\n<br />\n中共直接控制警隊，所以未來一哥人選一早就計劃好，點解搵劉業成返來做副處長負責平定示威，唔係因為未來一哥既能力問題，而係因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共推算過血腥鎮壓示威之後，一定會推人出來孭飛祭旗平息民憤</span></span></strong>，所以呢個位唔可以由未來一哥頂，呢個亦係警隊史無前例三個副處長既原因。<br />\n<br />\n亦因爲咁，前線跋扈濫權班popo，最終一定會俾中共推一堆出來祭旗。"},{"pid":"1bb471f93a0f0624aa9c8858cab878235a9dcc1b","tid":1545162,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:15:18.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcbc65bf34c99039d196d516ede1c964f52f2f3b","tid":1545162,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:15:32.000Z","msg":"907 機場攻略正式出爐，唔使再驚大逃走！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544251</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=